casebody.data:
No. —

Martínez v. Succession of González et al. Decided March 27, 1913. Mr. Santiago B. Palmer for respondents. Mr. Antonio Suliveres for appellant.

Appeal from the District Court of Arecibo. Motion of respondents, with the consent of the appellant, to dismiss appeal. Motion denied because it does not show the date of the judgment rendered by the lower court and the filing of the appeal therefrom.
